=Episode 21=

7
00:00:43,960 --> 00:00:44,759
Dongfang Yan!

8
00:00:46,280 --> 00:00:47,079
Xi?

9
00:00:50,240 --> 00:00:51,240
What's wrong with you?

10
00:00:52,640 --> 00:00:54,439
You look as if
you're here to get back at me.

11
00:00:57,399 --> 00:00:58,000
Mr. Yan.

12
00:00:58,719 --> 00:01:00,159
I'll tell you a bedtime story.

13
00:01:02,880 --> 00:01:04,239
It's getting late.

14
00:01:04,880 --> 00:01:06,319
You should head upstairs
and get some rest.

15
00:01:06,879 --> 00:01:08,000
It's just a story.

16
00:01:08,400 --> 00:01:09,359
What are you afraid of?

17
00:01:13,840 --> 00:01:14,560
Come.

18
00:01:14,920 --> 00:01:15,930
Are you going to walk yourself?

19
00:01:16,079 --> 00:01:17,200
Or, do you want me to carry you there?

20
00:01:19,799 --> 00:01:21,079
I'll just tell you a story.

21
00:01:21,959 --> 00:01:22,799
I'll go when I'm done.

22
00:01:33,359 --> 00:01:35,480
Once upon a time, there was a novel.

23
00:01:36,280 --> 00:01:38,439
It was equipped with a System
that controlled the plot.

24
00:01:39,439 --> 00:01:42,400
Stop reading those novels
Yang Xiaoxin sends you.

25
00:01:42,560 --> 00:01:43,400
Don't interrupt.

26
00:01:45,680 --> 00:01:47,959
The System was authoritarian.

27
00:01:49,400 --> 00:01:51,560
No matter how lousy the plot was,
it had to continue.

28
00:01:51,840 --> 00:01:53,560
It didn't care
about the characters' lives.

29
00:01:54,280 --> 00:01:56,400
It even enjoyed forcing things
that could never work out.

30
00:01:57,480 --> 00:01:58,599
It was utterly unreasonable,

31
00:01:58,850 --> 00:02:00,000
showing no regard for human rights.

32
00:02:01,599 --> 00:02:02,400
On top of that,

33
00:02:04,560 --> 00:02:05,879
it two-timed.

34
00:02:07,200 --> 00:02:08,280
No way.

35
00:02:08,800 --> 00:02:10,199
His match was the heroine,

36
00:02:10,199 --> 00:02:11,400
yet he said he liked me.

37
00:02:14,159 --> 00:02:15,400
He likes

38
00:02:16,280 --> 00:02:19,000
a charming and lovely villainess.

39
00:02:24,800 --> 00:02:25,680
Well...

40
00:02:27,680 --> 00:02:28,879
Is the System

41
00:02:28,879 --> 00:02:31,080
just toying

42
00:02:31,080 --> 00:02:32,199
with the villainess?

43
00:02:34,039 --> 00:02:37,199
Is he using the villainess

44
00:02:38,159 --> 00:02:40,080
to finish his storyline?

45
00:02:48,360 --> 00:02:49,120
Xi.

46
00:02:49,759 --> 00:02:51,159
Just like you said,

47
00:02:51,960 --> 00:02:53,960
