75
00:04:29,199 --> 00:04:30,546
(Countdown: 086)
This is the countdown for the bet

76
00:04:30,547 --> 00:04:32,439
(Countdown: 086)
between the villainess and the System.

77
00:04:35,399 --> 00:04:38,120
(Countdown: 085 days)
When this countdown reaches zero,

78
00:04:38,120 --> 00:04:41,720
